results.name: Triangle formed by reading the triangle of Eulerian numbers (A173018) mod 2.
comment: Apart from a shift in indexing, this is identical to Pascal's triangle mod 2, A047999.
xref: For the Eulerian triangle itself see A008292, A123125, A173018.
For the version in A173018 read mod m for m=2 through 10 see A290452-A290460. See also A047999.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Aug 05 2017
